<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ rạwyny yạ yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yạ rạwyny yạ yswʿ bḥnạnk ḥyạty hy rḍạk
 ạnt yạ rby frḥẗ qlby ạnạ ʿạysẖ hnạ bstnạk
 yạ rạfʿ rạsy fy ạlḍyq yạ mjdy yạ ạgẖly̱ ṣdyq
 yạ ḥbyby yạ mnwr ʿmry yạ fạdy yswʿ mạ ạḥlạk
 hllwyạ hllwyạ qlby tẖạbt wạnạ wyạk
 hllwyạ hllwyạ ạnạ ly mkạn fy smạk</lyrics>
